flowchart TD
    A[Scan IR line] --> B{Function definition?}
    B -->|Yes| C[Track function start]
    B -->|No| D{Entry label?}
    D -->|Yes| E[Mark ready for enter call]
    D -->|No| F{Phi or alloca?}
    F -->|Yes| G[Skip, continue scanning]
    F -->|No| H{First real instruction?}
    H -->|Yes| I[Insert enter call]
    H -->|No| J{Return instruction?}
    J -->|Yes| K[Insert exit call before return]
    J -->|No| L{Has debug location?}
    L -->|Yes| M{Safe to instrument?}
    M -->|Yes| N[Insert line call]
    M -->|No| O[Skip]
    L -->|No| O
